+
+config DRM_PANEL_BOE_TV101WUM_LL2
+	tristate "BOE TV101WUM LL2 1200x1920 panel"
+	depends on OF
+	depends on DRM_MIPI_DSI
+	depends on BACKLIGHT_CLASS_DEVICE
+	help
+	  Say Y here if you want to support for BOE TV101WUM-LL2
